-- ABB Wins Solar Power Plants Orders Valued at $50 Million in Western Sicily
-- Antonio Ligi
-- 2010-07-02T09:06:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/abb-wins-solar-power-plants-orders-valued-at-50-million-in-western-sicily.html

          
          
             ABB Ltd. won an order worth $50
million from Actelios SpA in Italy to supply three photovoltaic
solar power plants in western Sicily.  
 The order was booked in the second quarter, the Swiss
company said in an e-mailed statement.   
          
          


  


        